				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
							<p>The crypto market consists of a lot of small players and potential unicorns in the making. Because of this, public outlook on individual coins as well as the market itself is vital. Even more so than with Forex markets, this is a market of information and perception. This means, that prices are influenced by media coverage, government regulations and concerns over them, even statements from influencers in the crypto and business fields.<br /><br />Strong knowledge of the field and continuous research are the cornerstones of our investing approach, and this approach allows us to successfully trade cryptocurrencies in short term, making a sizeable profit on the volatility of the market.</p>						</div>
